animeTitle: Tatakau Mono-tachi e Ai wo Komete
animeDescription: Music video directed by Sou Ootsuki for the single Tatakau Mono-tachi e Ai wo Komete by the Japanese band Southern All Stars. It was later included in their two-disc studio album "Umi no Oh, Yeah!!"
